<h1>Gephex 0.4 Release Notes</h1>

<p>On June 6th 2004, the Gephex Project released Gephex 0.4.</p>

<p>Gephex is a modular real-time video effect framework.
Since the last stable relese (0.0.4), many bugs have been fixed,
effect-modules have been enhanced, and the usability has been
improved.</p>

